posting_body: ['PROP # 01K34', 'MIAMI: 4/2.5', 'Great rental opportunity.', 'Townhouse for rent in the fabulous community at Kendall Square.', '**4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, living, dining and comfortable family room with private access, blinds.', 'No rear neighbors.', 'Its features: granite countertop, stainless steel aplliances, wood cabinets, tile on the first floor and laminate upstairs (no carpet).', 'Entire unit freshly painted and LED cealing lamps.', 'Enjoy charter school inside the community and great clubhouse.', 'Easy access to 177 Ave (Krome Ave) and all the retails and commercial stores at 88 street.', 'Great location on the west side of Kendall Drive.', 'Read Less', 'Rent 1 Sale 1 Kendall', "Bad credit, no credit, come in we'll help you.", '*****', 'Se habla español *****', 'Interested in a property:', 'Call/Text-', 'show contact info', "786'+'7O8'+'2475", 'Call-', 'show contact info', "3O5'+'982'+'8O15", '**R1S1 -Kendall posts properties for a 30 day period of time.', 'Due to current high rental demand, some properties advertised may be withdrawn, canceled, rented, pending or sold within the past 30 days.', 'All information is deemed to be correct, but not guaranteed**', 'T a g s:', '- Kendall', '- Fontainebleau', '- West Fontainebleau', '- Dadeland']
